##My First Day at University

## Orientation and Campus Tour
– On the first day, we had an orientation where teachers explained the university rules and introduced different departments. We also went on a campus tour and saw important places like the library, labs, cafeteria, and classrooms. It helped me feel comfortable and know where everything is.

##Meeting New People
– I met many new classmates and senior students. Talking to them was fun and helped me make new friends. Seniors also gave useful tips about classes and campus life, which made me feel more confident.

## First Lecture
– I attended my first class in my chosen subject. The teacher explained the syllabus, assignments, and expectations. It was exciting to start learning and see what university academics are like.

